can neither read or write.

274
00:33:26,674 --> 00:33:28,075
I know it is hard.

275
00:33:30,678 --> 00:33:32,012
We are divided,

276
00:33:34,081 --> 00:33:36,183
but you do not despair,

277
00:33:37,217 --> 00:33:39,587
