478
00:57:47,668 --> 00:57:49,804
- Thank you very much.
- You're welcome.

479
00:57:50,805 --> 00:57:52,472
- For you, Father.
- Here.

480
00:57:52,573 --> 00:57:54,442
- Thank you.
